              <p>(Includes Novy home at 721 South Forest. Scenes from Whitmore Lake, Cavanaugh Lake, Winans Lake, and Frankfort. Campfire girls and camp scenes. Michigan Union Opera. Campus scenes. Neighborhood children shown are Margaret Cooley, daughter of Charles Horton Cooley, Gay Wilgus, daughter of Horace Wilgus, Evelyn Van Tyne, daughter of Claude Van Tyne, Julia Peterson, daughter of Reuben Peterson, Hester Reid, Margaret Henderson and the children of neighbor Victor Hugo Lane.)</p>
